Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:25.67,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.07,0:00:26.75,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Rinon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.53,0:00:30.55,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.82,0:00:35.09,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Kirishima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.75,0:00:37.49,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.49,0:00:38.01,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.50,0:00:40.70,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to your senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.50,0:00:43.15,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,I might not look it,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:45.31,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm pretty confident \Nin my ability to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.57,0:00:47.65,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Remon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.31,0:00:51.31,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:54.33,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Now then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.38,0:00:59.12,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,The first alien I met...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.52,0:01:01.08,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,She's very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.68,0:01:03.29,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,She's my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.83,0:01:06.69,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,And if you're going to \Ntry to get in her way...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.79,0:01:13.55,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to do \Nsomething you won't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.51,0:01:19.62,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Remon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.39,0:01:22.39,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:25.85,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:41.71,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't run anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.71,0:01:43.23,Natsu-Main,Manami,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.96,0:01:44.66,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.16,0:01:46.39,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Manami-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.39,0:01:47.38,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:51.32,Natsu-Main,Manami,0000,0000,0000,,My husband randomly told\Nme to come out here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:53.71,Natsu-Main,Manami,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:55.10,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Please drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.10,0:01:56.79,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,A stalker is chasing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.79,0:01:57.97,Natsu-Main,Manami,0000,0000,0000,,A stalker?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:02:00.48,Natsu-Main,Manami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make quick work of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.86,0:02:08.60,Natsu-Main,Manami,0000,0000,0000,,Your stalker's way too big!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.45,0:02:12.67,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Is it still following us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:14.77,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.77,0:02:15.48,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:17.71,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if everyone's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.71,0:02:20.86,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they're just about there by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:23.48,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'm sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:26.74,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:30.00,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:34.62,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Once we get over this mountain,\Nwe'll be at the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,0:02:35.71,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:37.84,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.14,0:02:38.76,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:39.65,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:44.97,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:46.26,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:50.39,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Rinna!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:51.96,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:55.07,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,So then... Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:59.46,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,There's an anti-field, so this \Nis about all I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.21,0:03:03.20,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.64,0:03:06.31,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you have \Nnothing left to regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:07.94,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:10.58,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,It's still...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:14.38,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Rinon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:17.29,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Rinon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:21.40,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Kaito-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:23.05,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.15,0:03:31.94,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Rinon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:42.86,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,This will take us to where we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:47.33,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,This is my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:50.41,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Because I was so selfish...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:52.58,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Tanigawa-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:53.83,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Ishigaki-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:54.67,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Kitahara-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:03:59.67,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Remon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:01.13,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Rinon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:05.35,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:07.26,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,You can't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:11.19,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone wants to make \Nyour dream a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:12.12,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:13.59,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,It's for all of us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:15.06,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to go to that place,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:17.50,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,find evidence of aliens,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:20.50,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,and then you won't have \Nto go back to space.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.90,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,We'll all be able to stay together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:27.03,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine. It'll go fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:36.58,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,If everything goes according to plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:41.51,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,maybe I'll be able to go \Nsee your planet someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:43.33,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,You want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:44.82,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:46.89,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know where you lived,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:49.27,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,and what your family's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:51.73,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I want to meet them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:55.87,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to introduce you to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.87,0:04:58.30,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,And who will you tell them I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.20,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:05.27,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could have introduced \Nyou to my parents, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.39,0:05:09.93,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,But it's fine. I have my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:13.30,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,But sometimes I wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:17.04,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,...that I could have made some more\Nmemories with everyone, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.06,0:05:23.37,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,But that's why I'm leaving lots \Nof things behind with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.37,0:05:25.66,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Even the smallest things,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:27.44,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,so at least I won't have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:32.33,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,You have a lot of \Nmemories in this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:33.50,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:38.87,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Tetsuro, Tanigawa, Kitahara, \NRemon-senpai, even my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:40.30,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:40.90,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:43.53,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. You're the heroine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:47.61,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I came to this planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:50.84,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:55.03,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I got to meet all of you, \Nhang out together, and make the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:57.54,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,All of it's just been so fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.13,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I want everything to stay this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:02.69,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I wish this summer wouldn't end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:06.15,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:11.54,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I fell in love, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.09,0:06:15.71,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Before I realized it, you \Nbecame my everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:18.40,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the same about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:22.50,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't all fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.01,0:06:24.59,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,There were hard times, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:26.86,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I was mad at times, and I cried at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:29.24,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be a lot more to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:31.74,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,We might end up fighting, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:33.37,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do if we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:35.56,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:36.73,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.55,0:06:42.33,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,You can overcome anything \Nas long as you're in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.68,0:06:47.67,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Will you love me forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:48.65,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:52.34,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in love with you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:53.72,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll love you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:06:56.33,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:07:00.57,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Could you say that one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:04.98,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.91,0:07:08.24,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I will love you forever, Kaito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:09.65,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:16.72,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,So love me forever, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:20.23,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:23.15,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:33.76,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty tough, as expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:36.84,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't give up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:43.40,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Took you long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:53.60,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Tetsuro-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:54.82,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:56.26,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,We're out of gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:59.01,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:02.29,Natsu-Main,Satoshi,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:03.70,Natsu-Main,Satoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Tetsuro-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:04.59,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.59,0:08:06.38,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Satoshi-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:08.38,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Satoshi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:09.55,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Manami-san's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:12.73,Natsu-Main,Manami,0000,0000,0000,,Save me, Satoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:16.89,Natsu-Main,Manami,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:24.93,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:28.43,Natsu-Main,Manami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but let's keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:48.92,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,It...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:52.13,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,It really existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.56,0:08:53.53,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:55.52,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:08:58.73,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,The place in the image I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:01.10,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I finally made it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:03.45,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:07.60,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kaito-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.09,0:09:09.06,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.33,0:09:12.86,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, let's start looking for proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:13.64,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.13,0:09:19.07,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:20.52,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.52,0:09:21.83,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,That's from the aliens?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.99,0:09:25.93,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,But this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:34.85,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,The way it reacted... That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:36.57,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:42.84,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:44.81,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,S-Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:46.89,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:48.15,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,You can see it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:48.94,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:52.96,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,But this is the image in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.96,0:09:56.17,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,The cells I used to heal him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:09.18,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,This is... the proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:15.59,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:25.85,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:27.59,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:29.56,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,We came all this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:31.81,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,All this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:36.24,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.75,0:10:38.70,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,The place Ichika and the \Nothers were heading to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:41.42,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,Did they break the spacial shielding?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.61,0:10:44.79,Natsu-Italic,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad, Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.69,0:10:48.50,Natsu-Italic,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and get out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:54.96,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:56.92,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.29,0:10:58.26,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:11:00.02,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hurt him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.46,0:11:03.14,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I won't run anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:05.09,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,No, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.94,0:11:08.17,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.17,0:11:09.68,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.68,0:11:10.77,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:12.26,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.26,0:11:14.07,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Kaito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:16.77,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do this anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.77,0:11:17.37,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,What are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:18.53,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,This is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:23.45,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,You're in danger! Everyone's \Nin danger because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:27.17,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,This is all because I was being selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.17,0:11:28.16,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.67,0:11:30.48,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,No, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:31.79,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.34,0:11:36.46,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone... At least I know I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:39.45,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:43.26,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,If anything, I'm the one being selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:46.40,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to let you go, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.74,0:11:54.15,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kaito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:55.54,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:11:57.31,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:12:01.11,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,...almost regretted coming to this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:05.37,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I got everyone caught up in\Ndoing what I wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:09.37,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,And in the end, I didn't achieve anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:12.87,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,But now I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:18.46,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,We found each other because we\Nall wanted something to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:21.12,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to find each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.67,0:12:28.97,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I will always have this \Nfeeling within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.61,0:12:31.19,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,It'll never disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:32.39,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I can believe in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:35.65,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.27,0:12:38.48,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Kaito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:43.47,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I will always... always...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:45.75,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Sen—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.52,0:12:50.45,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:52.48,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I'll come get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:55.91,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.79,0:13:02.31,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.15,0:13:03.98,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Kai—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:27.13,Natsu-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how long it's been.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.46,0:13:31.33,Natsu-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,But thank you for finding this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:35.12,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it directly \Nfrom the In-Grove...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:38.56,Natsu-Main,BG Voice,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I made an emergency \Nlanding on this planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:38.86,Natsu-Main,Emika,0000,0000,0000,,The data our ancestors passed \Ndown to us has been released.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:40.58,Natsu-Main,BG Voice,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}after my spaceship had trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.58,0:13:43.59,Natsu-Main,BG Voice,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}and was saved by someone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.07,0:13:48.15,Natsu-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Before I knew it, he meant a lot to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.15,0:13:51.02,Natsu-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a remote planet
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:54.16,Natsu-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,where contact with\Nthe locals is forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:56.30,Natsu-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Help will soon be on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:14:01.95,Natsu-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,I imagine my memories on this planet\Nwill be sealed to maintain secrecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:05.69,Natsu-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,But... I wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:08.62,Natsu-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,...to leave behind the memories\NI had with him, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:11.97,Natsu-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Even if my memories faded,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:14.02,Natsu-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,even if I couldn't remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:15.91,Natsu-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to leave something behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:18.86,Natsu-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for finding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.86,0:14:23.49,Natsu-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,I pray that at least my \Nmemories will live on in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:27.05,Natsu-Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.52,0:14:29.84,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:32.85,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I could never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:38.99,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:44.48,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,It was only a few months.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.79,0:14:44.48,Sign12F,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Uminokuchi Station
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:46.94,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Something that happened one summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:52.02,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Back then we still hadn't done anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:55.49,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,But we wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:14:59.54,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,And that's when Ichika-senpai \Nappeared before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.22,0:15:04.33,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,And made our summer special for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:07.47,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Joy and sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:09.38,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,All of it was there,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:10.72,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,in that summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:12.46,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:18.68,Natsu-Ep-Title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 12\NWaiting there, in the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:17.72,Natsu-Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,...will never forget that summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.19,0:15:34.66,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Tetsuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:35.73,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:37.84,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,A girl in the class next door \Nasked me to give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:40.49,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.49,0:15:41.75,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:44.45,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you give her an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.45,0:15:47.41,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, get a girlfriend already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:49.63,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.96,0:15:52.18,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Mio's good enough, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:53.58,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I'd welcome you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:56.67,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:15:59.95,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Don't laugh, Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:05.01,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:06.52,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful heading back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:07.41,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:09.33,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:11.33,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:14.69,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:16.28,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.38,0:16:19.29,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.12,0:16:27.88,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.37,0:16:29.83,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Did I forget to lock it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.83,0:16:31.26,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.35,0:16:33.58,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.58,0:16:35.05,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:37.76,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,How was Bolivia?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:40.18,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,It was a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:42.01,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,But it was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:43.19,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:44.48,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:46.29,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Here are your souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:49.19,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I question your taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:50.02,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:53.87,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,The doll is famous over there for \Nbeing able to grant wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.87,0:16:56.16,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,And this is for Ichika-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:16:59.77,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, where is Ichika-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.13,0:17:04.37,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,H-Her period for studying abroad ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:07.27,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,She went back to her homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:10.88,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:12.95,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:16.71,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can send it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.71,0:17:18.50,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You know her address, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.96,0:17:24.56,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:40.37,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:42.62,Natsu-Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:45.24,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,You're transferring?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.24,0:17:48.21,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, family issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.43,0:17:51.17,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't leave, too—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:56.88,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,So when are you transferring?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:58.14,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.42,0:17:59.51,Natsu-Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.90,0:18:02.13,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a farewell gift or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:03.41,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,but this is for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:04.52,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:07.81,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:10.34,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Film?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.83,0:18:11.76,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Why—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:13.47,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.18,0:18:15.84,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Remon-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:19.82,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,That was truly a wonderful summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:21.77,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:25.87,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,...the film is incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:30.54,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who has to put the\Nfinishing touches on the last scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:34.51,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about this, Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:36.07,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,We came over all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:36.99,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:38.22,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,My sister's going to be \Nhome late today, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.19,0:18:44.59,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,But it's been a while since\Nwe've all been here together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:47.27,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to turn off the lights, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:47.94,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.97,0:18:54.77,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:56.99,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,You good?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:04.37,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.02,0:19:14.75,Sign12A,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Remon Yamano
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.02,0:19:14.75,Sign12B,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Unfinished Production
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:02.50,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,People say that when someone\Ndies, they can go to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.51,0:21:06.35,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think that's the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:09.42,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,When someone dies,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.42,0:21:13.13,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that person journeys \Ninto people's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:18.50,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,They live on as a memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.03,0:21:28.35,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,But that, too, will eventually wane.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.76,0:21:32.81,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,That's why people desire to leave \Nsomething behind in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:36.31,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,So others won't forget them,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:38.02,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,so we'll remember them...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:41.77,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep filming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.18,0:21:46.45,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Recording the continuation \Nto what I have on film,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:49.58,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,the continuation to that summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.39,0:22:24.61,Sign12C,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Special Consultant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.65,0:22:51.25,Sign12G,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1082,1)}Violet Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.23,0:22:53.97,Natsu-Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,They're playing this \Nmovie again this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.49,0:22:56.93,Natsu-Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the one that \Nthe alumni left behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.93,0:22:59.44,Natsu-Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it last year. It was pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.77,0:23:02.69,Natsu-Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,There was a spaceship and \Na mech. Lots of SFX.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:04.23,Natsu-Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The heroine's a hottie.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.23,0:23:05.69,Natsu-Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you gotta bring up?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.21,0:23:09.75,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,You have no place to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.75,0:23:11.20,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:15.91,Sign12D,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Movie in Session
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:15.91,Sign12D,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Annual \N"Waiting in the Summer" \NShowing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.58,0:23:14.46,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about you come to my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.46,0:23:15.91,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I live on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.36,0:23:18.34,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,So I have extra rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.34,0:23:21.19,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your spaceship?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.19,0:23:23.13,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It broke?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.64,0:23:24.69,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.09,0:23:41.39,Sign12E,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,751)}Thank You Very Much
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.83,0:23:36.48,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you all for your support!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.48,0:23:38.31,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
